Dishes.name: Caffe Americano
Dishes.description: Espresso shots topped with hot water create a light layer of crema culminating in this wonderfully rich cup with depth and nuance. Pro tip: For an additional boost, ask to try this with an extra shot.

Dishes.name: Caffe Misto
Dishes.description: A 1-to-1 combination of fresh-brewed coffee and steamed milk add up to one distinctly delicious coffee drink that's remarkably mixed.

Dishes.name: Blonde Roast Coffee
Dishes.description: Lightly roasted coffee that's soft, mellow and flavorful. Easy-drinking on its own and delicious with milk, sugar or flavored with vanilla, caramel or hazelnut.

Dishes.name: Featured Starbucks Dark Roast Coffee
Dishes.description: This full-bodied dark roast coffee with bold, robust flavors showcases our roasting and blending artistry—an essential blend of balanced and lingering flavors.

Dishes.name: Pike Place Roast Coffee
Dishes.description: From our first store in Seattle's Pike Place Market to our coffeehouses around the world, customers requested a freshly brewed coffee they could enjoy throughout the day. In 2008 our master blenders and roasters created this for you—a smooth, well-rounded blend of Latin American coffees with subtly rich flavors of chocolate and toasted nuts, it's served fresh every day at a Starbucks store near you.

Dishes.name: Decaf Pike Place Roast Coffee
Dishes.description: From our first store in Seattle's Pike Place Market to our coffeehouses around the world, customers requested a freshly brewed coffee they could enjoy throughout the day. In 2008 our master blenders and roasters created this for you—a smooth, well-rounded blend of Latin American coffees with subtly rich flavors of chocolate and toasted nuts, it's served fresh every day at a Starbucks store near you. (Decaf as you like it.)

Dishes.name: Cappuccino
Dishes.description: Dark, rich espresso lies in wait under a smoothed and stretched layer of thick milk foam. An alchemy of barista artistry and craft.

Dishes.name: Espresso
Dishes.description: Our smooth signature Espresso Roast with rich flavor and caramelly sweetness is at the very heart of everything we do.

Dishes.name: Espresso con Panna
Dishes.description: Espresso meets a dollop of whipped cream to enhance the rich and caramelly flavors of a straight-up shot.

Dishes.name: Flat White
Dishes.description: Smooth ristretto shots of espresso get the perfect amount of steamed whole milk to create a not-too-strong, not-too-creamy, just-right flavor.

Dishes.name: Honey Almondmilk Flat White
Dishes.description: This flat white intentionally pairs almondmilk and Starbucks signature espresso roast with a hint of honey, making a perfect amount of creamy, nutty sweetness.

Dishes.name: Honey Oatmilk Latte
Dishes.description: Oat milk and signature espresso are intentionally combined with a hint of honey and a toasted honey topping—a savory tribute to all things sweet and salty.

Dishes.name: Caffe Latte
Dishes.description: Our dark, rich espresso balanced with steamed milk and a light layer of foam. A perfect milk-forward warm-up.

Dishes.name: Cinnamon Dolce Latte
Dishes.description: We add freshly steamed milk and cinnamon dolce-flavored syrup to our classic espresso, topped with sweetened whipped cream and a cinnamon dolce topping to bring you specialness in a treat.

Dishes.name: Starbucks Blonde Vanilla Latte
Dishes.description: Extra-smooth Starbucks Blonde Espresso, velvety steamed milk and vanilla syrup come together to create a delightful new twist on a beloved espresso classic. An ideal cup for those who prefer a lighter-roasted coffee.

Dishes.name: Caramel Macchiato
Dishes.description: Freshly steamed milk with vanilla-flavored syrup marked with espresso and topped with a caramel drizzle for an oh-so-sweet finish.

Dishes.name: Espresso Macchiato
Dishes.description: Our rich espresso marked with dollop of steamed milk and foam. A European-style classic.

Dishes.name: Caffe Mocha
Dishes.description: Our rich, full-bodied espresso combined with bittersweet mocha sauce and steamed milk, then topped with sweetened whipped cream. The classic coffee drink that always sweetly satisfies.

Dishes.name: White Chocolate Mocha
Dishes.description: Our signature espresso meets white chocolate sauce and steamed milk, and then is finished off with sweetened whipped cream to create this supreme white chocolate delight.

Dishes.name: Chai Tea Latte
Dishes.description: Black tea infused with cinnamon, clove and other warming spices is combined with steamed milk and topped with foam for the perfect balance of sweet and spicy. An iconic chai cup.

Dishes.name: Chai Tea
Dishes.description: Black tea infused with warm clove, cardamom, cinnamon and ginger notes. A bold, distinctive chai tea.

Dishes.name: Earl Grey Tea
Dishes.description: We take a strong black tea base and add the essence of bergamot, a citrus fruit with subtle lemon and floral lavender notes, to create this aromatically awesome tea flavor.

Dishes.name: London Fog Tea Latte
Dishes.description: Bright, citrusy spark of Italian bergamot blends with subtle hints of lavender, vanilla syrup and steamed milk for this frothy reinvention of classic Earl Grey tea.

Dishes.name: Royal English Breakfast Tea
Dishes.description: Each sip of this beloved morning black tea unfolds to reveal the complexity of the high-grown full leaves. An elegant, time-honored classic that brings a royal nod to every cup.

Dishes.name: Royal English Breakfast Tea Latte
Dishes.description: A select blend of rich, full-leaf black teas from India and Sri Lanka sweetened with liquid cane sugar and topped with steamed milk and a velvety foam. Each and every sip—smooth and silky.

Dishes.name: Emperor's Clouds & Mist Tea
Dishes.description: This gently smoky, softly sweet green tea—cultivated at 3,500 feet and shrouded in ethereal clouds and mist—is tasty no matter what language you say it in.

Dishes.name: Matcha Tea Latte
Dishes.description: Smooth and creamy matcha sweetened just right and served with steamed milk. This favorite will transport your senses to pure green delight.

Dishes.name: Honey Citrus Mint Tea
Dishes.description: A customer creation so popular it’s now on the menu. Jade Citrus Mint green tea, Peach Tranquility herbal tea, hot water, steamed lemonade and a touch of honey mingle tastefully well together for a tea that comforts from the inside out.

Dishes.name: Jade Citrus Mint Brewed Tea
Dishes.description: Green tea, lemon verbena, lemongrass and a hint of spearmint mingle for a bright, refreshing, citrusy green tea experience.

Dishes.name: Mint Majesty
Dishes.description: A blend of mint and a pinch of lemon verbena creates a refreshing flavor that's supercool for a caffeine-free herbal tea.

Dishes.name: Peach Tranquility
Dishes.description: A sweet fusion of peach, candied pineapple, chamomile blossoms, lemon verbena and rose hips come together in this caffeine-free herbal tea. Sip back and relax.

Dishes.name: Hot Chocolate
Dishes.description: Steamed milk with vanilla and chocolate-flavored syrups. Topped with sweetened whipped cream and chocolate-flavored drizzle. A timeless classic made to sweeten your spirits.

Dishes.name: White Hot Chocolate
Dishes.description: A traditional hot chocolate beverage made with white chocolate sauce and steamed milk. Topped with whipped cream.

Dishes.name: Caramel Apple Spice
Dishes.description: Steamed apple juice complemented with cinnamon syrup, whipped cream and a caramel sauce drizzle.

Dishes.name: Steamed Apple Juice
Dishes.description: Freshly steamed 100% apple juice (not from concentrate). Feel the apple goodness in this classic fruit drink that will soothe and embolden your day.

Dishes.name: Cinnamon Dolce Creme
Dishes.description: We combine freshly steamed milk and cinnamon dolce–flavored syrup. Topped with sweetened whipped cream and a cinnamon dolce topping to give you a creamy, special treat.

Dishes.name: Steamed Milk
Dishes.description: Enjoy a warm cup of skim, 2%, soy, almond or coconut milk steamed for your sipping pleasure.

Dishes.name: Vanilla Creme
Dishes.description: A smooth, frothy vanilla-flavored luxury. For those times, when you'd rather not indulge in the rich flavor of our world-famous espresso, but desire a hot, creamy vanilla beverage.

Dishes.name: Espresso Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Coffee is combined with a shot of espresso and milk, then blended with ice to give you a nice little jolt and lots of sipping joy.

Dishes.name: Mocha Cookie Crumble Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Frappuccino Roast Coffee, mocha sauce and Frappuccino chips blended with milk and ice, layered on top of whipped cream and chocolate cookie crumble and topped with vanilla whipped cream, mocha drizzle and even more chocolate cookie crumble. Each sip is as good as the last...all the way to the end.

Dishes.name: Caramel Ribbon Crunch Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Buttery caramel syrup blended with coffee, milk and ice, then topped with a layer of dark caramel sauce, whipped cream, caramel drizzle and a crunchy caramel-sugar topping—oh-so-beautifully delicious.

Dishes.name: Caffe Vanilla Frappuccino
Dishes.description: We take Frappuccino Roast Coffee and vanilla bean powder, combine them with milk and ice, and top it with whipped cream. Tastes like happiness.

Dishes.name: Coffee Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Coffee meets milk and ice in a blender for a rumble-and-tumble togetherness to create one of our most-beloved original Frappuccino blended beverages.

Dishes.name: Caramel Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Caramel syrup meets coffee, milk and ice for a rendezvous in the blender, while whipped cream and buttery caramel sauce layer the love on top. To change things up, try it affogato-style with a hot espresso shot poured right over the top.

Dishes.name: Mocha Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Mocha sauce, Frappuccino Roast Coffee, milk and ice all come together for a mocha flavor that'll leave you wanting more. To change things up, try it affogato-style with a hot espresso shot poured right over the top.

Dishes.name: Java Chip Frappuccino
Dishes.description: We blend mocha sauce and Frappuccino chips with coffee, milk and ice, then top it off with whipped cream and a mocha drizzle to bring you endless java joy.

Dishes.name: White Chocolate Mocha Frappuccino
Dishes.description: White chocolate Frappuccino Roast Coffee, milk and ice get together for what might be the best thing that happens to you all day. Oh, and there's whipped cream on top.

Dishes.name: Chocolate Cookie Crumble Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Mocha sauce and Frappuccino chips are blended with milk and ice, layered on top of whipped cream and chocolate cookie crumble and topped with vanilla whipped cream, mocha drizzle and even more chocolate cookie crumble. These layers ensure each sip is as good as the last...all the way to the end.

Dishes.name: Caramel Ribbon Crunch Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Buttery caramel syrup is blended with milk and ice, then topped with a layer of dark caramel sauce, whipped cream, caramel drizzle and a crunchy caramel-sugar topping—oh-so-beautifully delicious.

Dishes.name: Strawberry Crème Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Summer's favorite berry is the star of this delicious Frappuccino Blended Beverage—a blend of ice, milk and strawberry puree layered on top of a splash of strawberry puree and finished with vanilla whipped cream.

Dishes.name: Chai Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Rich mocha-flavored sauce meets up with chocolaty chips, milk and ice for a blender bash. Top it off with sweetened whipped cream and mocha drizzle for a real party in your mouth.

Dishes.name: Double Chocolaty Chip Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: Rich mocha-flavored sauce meets up with chocolaty chips, milk and ice for a blender bash. Top it off with sweetened whipped cream and mocha drizzle for a real party in your mouth.

Dishes.name: Matcha Green Tea Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: This blend of sweetened premium matcha green tea, milk and ice— topped off with sweetened whipped cream—inspires a delicious boost and good green vibes.

Dishes.name: Vanilla Bean Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: This rich and creamy blend of vanilla bean, milk and ice topped with whipped cream takes va-va-vanilla flavor to another level. To change things up, try it affogato-style with a hot espresso shot poured right over the top.

Dishes.name: White Chocolate Creme Frappuccino
Dishes.description: A smooth blend of white chocolate sauce, milk and ice topped with whipped cream for a remarkable flavor that surprisingly wows.

Dishes.name: Chocolate Java Mint Frappuccino® Blended Beverage
Dishes.description: Coffee and flavors of sweet chocolate and refreshing mint blended with rich Frappuccino® chips for a smooth treat finished with a layer of mocha sauce, whipped cream and chocolate-mint cookie crumble.

Dishes.name: Honey Almondmilk Cold Brew
Dishes.description: Starbucks Cold Brew lightly sweetened with honey and topped off with almondmilk for a balanced taste in every delicious sip.

Dishes.name: Iced Brown Sugar Oatmilk Shaken Espresso
Dishes.description: First we shake Starbucks Blonde espresso, brown sugar and cinnamon together, and then top it off with oatmilk and ice for a cool lift to power you through your day.

Dishes.name: Iced Toasted Vanilla Oatmilk Shaken Espresso
Iced Shaken Espresso
Dishes.description: Made with the rich, full-bodied espresso you love—then shaken, chilled and mellowed with sweetness and a touch of milk to create a delightfully and deliciously convenient on-the-go drink.

Dishes.name: Chocolate Cream Cold Brew
Dishes.description: Starbucks cold brew sweetened with vanilla syrup and topped with a silky, chocolaty cream cold foam.

Dishes.name: Salted Caramel Cream Cold Brew
Dishes.description: Here's a savory-meets-sweet refreshing beverage certain to delight: our signature, super-smooth cold brew, sweetened with a touch of caramel and topped with a salted, rich cold foam.

Dishes.name: Starbucks Cold Brew Coffee
Dishes.description: Handcrafted in small batches daily, slow-steeped in cool water for 20 hours without touching heat—Starbucks Cold Brew is made from our custom blend of beans grown to steep long and cold for a super-smooth flavor.

Dishes.name: Starbucks Cold Brew Coffee with Milk
Dishes.description: Handcrafted in small batches daily, slow-steeped in cool water for 20 hours, without touching heat and finished with a splash of milk—Starbucks Cold Brew is made from our custom blend of beans grown to steep long and cold for a super-smooth flavor.

Dishes.name: Iced Caffe Americano
Dishes.description: Espresso shots topped with cold water produce a light layer of crema that is then served over ice. The result: A wonderfully rich cup with depth and nuance. Pro tip: For an additional boost, try this with an extra shot.

Dishes.name: Iced Coffee
Dishes.description: Freshly brewed Starbucks Iced Coffee Blend served chilled and sweetened over ice. An absolutely, seriously, refreshingly lift to any day.

Dishes.name: Iced Coffee with Milk
Dishes.description: Freshly brewed Starbucks Iced Coffee Blend with milk served chilled and sweetened over ice. An absolutely, seriously, refreshingly lift to any day.

Dishes.name: Iced Espresso
Dishes.description: Our smooth signature Espresso Roast over ice boasts rich, robust flavor and caramelly sweetness. A recipe of perfection at the heart of every handcrafted espresso we serve.

Dishes.name: Iced Flat White
Dishes.description: Smooth ristretto shots of espresso get the perfect amount of whole milk and ice to create a not-too-strong, not-too-creamy, just-right flavor.

Dishes.name: Iced Honey Almondmilk Flat White
Dishes.description: This iced flat white intentionally made with almondmilk and Starbucks Blonde Espresso Roast poured over ice with a hint of honey-creates a perfect amount of cool, creamy, nutty sweetness.

Dishes.name: Iced Honey Oatmilk Latte
Dishes.description: Oat milk and signature espresso are intentionally combined over ice with a hint of honey and a toasted honey topping—a savory tribute to all things sweet and salty.

Dishes.name: Iced Caffe Latte
Dishes.description: Our dark, rich espresso combined with milk and served over ice. A perfect milk-forward cool-down.

Dishes.name: Iced Cinnamon Dolce Latte
Dishes.description: We add freshly steamed milk and cinnamon dolce-flavored syrup to our classic espresso and ice, topped with sweetened whipped cream and a cinnamon dolce topping to bring you specialness in a treat.

Dishes.name: Iced Starbucks Blonde Vanilla Latte
Dishes.description: Seriously smooth and subtly sweet Starbucks Blonde Espresso, milk, ice and vanilla syrup come together to create a delightful twist on a beloved espresso classic.

Dishes.name: Iced Caramel Macchiato
Dishes.description: We combine our rich, full-bodied espresso with vanilla-flavored syrup, milk and ice, then top it off with a caramel drizzle for an oh-so-sweet finish.

Dishes.name: Iced Caffe Mocha
Dishes.description: Our rich, full-bodied espresso combined with bittersweet mocha sauce, milk and ice, then topped with sweetened whipped cream. The classic iced coffee drink that always sweetly satisfies.

Dishes.name: Iced White Chocolate Mocha
Dishes.description: Our signature espresso meets white chocolate sauce, milk and ice, and then is finished off with sweetened whipped cream to create this supreme white chocolate delight.

Dishes.name: Cinnamon Caramel Cream Cold Brew
Dishes.description: Starbucks® Cold Brew packed with flavors of cinnamon caramel, topped with vanilla sweet cream cold foam and dusted with even more flavour for a special personal treat.

Dishes.name: White Chocolate Macadamia Cream Cold Brew
Dishes.description: Starbucks® signature cold brew sweetened with macadamia syrup, topped with a silky white-chocolate macadamia cream cold foam and finished with toasted cookie crumbles.

Dishes.name: Vanilla Sweet Cream Cold Brew
Dishes.description: Our slow-steeped custom blend of Starbucks Cold Brew coffee accented with vanilla and topped with a delicate float of house-made vanilla sweet cream that cascades throughout the cup. It's over-the-top and super-smooth.

Dishes.name: Iced Pineapple Matcha with Coconut Milk
Dishes.description: Our premium matcha green tea shaken with flavors of pineapple and ginger along with coconut milk and ice for a delicious beverage to uplift your day.

Dishes.name: Mango Dragonfruit Starbucks Refresher
Dishes.description: This tropical-inspired pick-me-up—crafted with a refreshing combination of sweet mango and dragonfruit flavors—is hand-shaken with ice and a scoop of real diced dragonfruit. Contains caffeine.

Dishes.name: Mango Dragonfruit Lemonade Starbucks Refresher
Dishes.description: This tropical-inspired pick-me-up—crafted with a clever combination of vibrant lemonade, sweet mango and refreshing dragonfruit flavors—is hand-shaken with ice and a scoop of real diced dragonfruit. Contains caffeine.

Dishes.name: Strawberry Acai Starbucks Refresher
Dishes.description: Sweet strawberry flavors accented by passion fruit and acai notes, and caffeinated with green coffee extract—a welcoming sweet spot of refreshment.

Dishes.name: Strawberry Acai Lemonade Starbucks Refresher
Dishes.description: Sweet strawberry flavors, passion fruit and acai notes balanced with the delightful zing of lemonade and  caffeine from green coffee extract. Served over ice. This is the ultimate pick-me-up your afternoon is calling for.

Dishes.name: Dragon Drink
Dishes.description: This tropical-inspired pick-me-up—crafted with a refreshing combination of sweet mango and dragonfruit flavors—is hand-shaken with creamy coconut milk, ice and a scoop of real diced dragonfruit. Contains caffeine.

Dishes.name: Pink Drink
Dishes.description: Our crisp Strawberry Acai Refresher with its accents of passion fruit, is combined with creamy coconut milk. A fruity and refreshing sip of spring, no matter what time of year.

Dishes.name: Evolution Fresh Organic Vital Berry
Dishes.description: Bright berries, orange and mango blend together for a satisfying smoothie with a delicious punch of vitamin-C.

Dishes.name: Evolution Fresh Organic Defense Up
Dishes.description: A refreshing smoothie packed with bright flavor thanks to organic oranges, pineapples, mangoes, apples and acerola cherries. An excellent source of vitamin-C, made with 100% juice and no added sweeteners or artificial flavors.

Dishes.name: Evolution Fresh Orange
Dishes.description: Once you try this orange juice—cold-pressed with oranges picked and squeezed at their peak of sweetness—you'll never go back to any other. Vitamin-C-packed and made with 100% juice, no added sweeteners or any artificial flavors.

Dishes.name: Evolution Fresh Organic Super Fruit Greens
Dishes.description: Here's a satisfying way to get your greens: A fruit and vegetable smoothie packed with goodness including mango puree, spinach, spirulina, chlorella and vitamin-C. Made with 100% juice and no added sweeteners or artificial flavors.

Dishes.name: Evolution Fresh Watermelon
Dishes.description: A naturally refreshing and hydrating juice with just a touch of lemon and just the right amount of watermelon picked at its absolute peak of sweetness, then cold-pressed for maximum flavor and nutrients. 100% juice with no added sweeteners or artificial flavors.

Dishes.name: Tree Top Apple Juice Box
Dishes.description: This childhood favorite contains 100% of your daily vitamin-C with just the right amount of sweetness.

Dishes.name: Lemonade
Dishes.description: Awaken your taste buds with the zing of refreshing lemonade—this tangy, fresh sip puts a little zip in your step.

Dishes.name: Blended Strawberry Lemonade
Dishes.description: Awaken your taste buds with the zing of refreshing lemonade infused with a hint of delicious strawberry flavor and blended with ice. A light, fresh beverage that puts a little zip in your step.

Dishes.name: Horizon Organic Chocolate Milk Box
Dishes.description: Great for snacks, travel and more, this chocolate organic milk box is a convenient way to experience your milk on the go and everywhere.

Dishes.name: Horizon Organic Low-Fat Milk Box
Dishes.description: Great for snacks, travel and more, this organic low-fat milk box is a convenient way to experience your milk on the go and everywhere.

Dishes.name: Horizon Organic Vanilla Milk Box
Dishes.description: Grab a mini carton of organic milk to complement a treat from our pastry case or pack into a lunch bag. Enjoy a sip and a touch of tasty vanilla.

Dishes.name: Galvanina Sparkling Water
Dishes.description: The essential refresher. Our sparking, natural mineral water will quench your thirst with effervescent ease.

Dishes.name: Galvanina Lime Sparkling Water
Dishes.description: Natural, thirst-quenching mineral water with a twist of refreshing lime.

Dishes.name: Spindrift Grapefruit Sparkling Water
Dishes.description: Pink, tangy grapefruits squeezed into sparkling water—along with touches of orange and lemon—for an effervescent, delightfully refreshing beverage.

Dishes.name: Spindrift Raspberry Lime Sparkling Water
Dishes.description: Raspberry and lime squeezed into sparkling water for an effervescent, delightfully refreshing beverage.

Dishes.name: Ethos Bottled Water
Dishes.description: For every bottle of Ethos water you buy, Starbucks will donate 5 cents to support humanitarian programs in coffee-growing communities, providing clean, safe water to those in need.

Dishes.name: Water
Dishes.description: The essential refresher.

Dishes.name: Hawai‘i Volcanic Bottled Water
Dishes.description: Hawaii's signature natural artesian water from the Big Island—rejuvenating and replenishing.

Dishes.name: Paradise Drink Starbucks Refreshers® Beverage
Dishes.description: Tropical flavors of pineapple and passionfruit combine with diced pineapple and creamy coconut beverage to create a delicious island escape.

Dishes.name: Pineapple Passionfruit Starbucks Refreshers® Beverage
Dishes.description: Tropical flavors of pineapple and passionfruit mix with diced pineapple to create an island escape––oh so refreshing.

Dishes.name: Pineapple Passionfruit Lemonade Starbucks Refreshers® Beverage
Dishes.description: Tropical flavors of pineapple and passionfruit combine with diced pineapple and refreshing lemonade to create a taste of sunshine in a cup.

Dishes.name: Iced Black Tea
Dishes.description: Premium black tea is sweetened just right and shaken with ice. It's the ideal iced tea—a rich and flavorful black tea journey awaits you.

Dishes.name: Iced Black Tea Lemonade
Dishes.description: Premium black tea is sweetened just right, then shaken with refreshing lemonade and ice for this Arnold Palmer–inspired beverage. A distinguished, satisfying treat.

Dishes.name: Iced London Fog Tea Latte
Dishes.description: Bright, citrusy spark of bergamot blends with subtle hints of lavender and mixes with vanilla syrup, milk and ice to create this delicious reinvention of a classic Earl Grey tea.

Dishes.name: Iced Chai Tea Latte
Dishes.description: Black tea infused with cinnamon, clove and other warming spices are combined with milk and ice for the perfect balance of sweet and spicy.

Dishes.name: Iced Peach Green Tea
Dishes.description: This boldly flavored iced tea—made with a combination of our peach-flavored fruit juice blend and Teavana iced green tea, and then sweetened with liquid cane sugar and hand-shaken with ice—brings you refreshing vibes.

Dishes.name: Iced Peach Green Tea Lemonade
Dishes.description: This boldly refreshing iced tea is made with a combination of our peach-flavored fruit juice blend, Teavana iced green tea and lemonade, then sweetened with liquid cane sugar and hand-shaken with ice.

Dishes.name: Iced Matcha Green Tea Latte
Dishes.description: Smooth and creamy matcha sweetened just right and served with milk over ice. Green has never tasted so good.

Dishes.name: Iced Green Tea
Dishes.description: Green tea blended with mint, lemongrass and lemon verbena, then sweetened just right and given a good shake with ice. Lightly flavored and oh-so-refreshing!

Dishes.name: Iced Green Tea Lemonade
Dishes.description: Green tea blended with mint, lemongrass, lemon verbena and lemonade, then sweetened just right and given a good shake with ice. Lightly flavored and oh-so-refreshing!

Dishes.name: Matcha Lemonade
Dishes.description: Our finely ground Teavana matcha green tea combined with crisp lemonade, then shaken with ice, creates a refreshingly sweet, delicious drink that's a delightfully vibrant, green-hue.

Dishes.name: Iced Passion Tango Tea
Dishes.description: A blend of hibiscus, lemongrass and apple sweetened just right and hand-shaken with ice. A refreshingly vibrant tea infused with the color of passion.

Dishes.name: Iced Passion Tango Tea Lemonade
Dishes.description: Our blend of hibiscus, lemongrass and apple sweetened just right and hand-shaken with ice, lemonade and, of course, passion.

Dishes.name: Bacon, Sausage & Egg Wrap
Dishes.description: Delicious double-smoked bacon, savory sausage and cage-free scrambled eggs, combined with cheddar cheese and sous vide potatoes all wrapped in a flour tortilla for a breakfast you’re sure to love.

Dishes.name: Impossible Breakfast Sandwich
Dishes.description: The savory Impossible plant-based sausage patty, combined with a cage-free fried egg and aged cheddar cheese on an artisanal ciabatta bread. It’s everything you love about a classic sausage breakfast sandwich but now with plant-based sausage.

Dishes.name: Spinach, Feta & Cage-Free Egg White Wrap
Dishes.description: We bring together cage-free egg whites, spinach, feta cheese and tomatoes inside a whole wheat wrap, then toast it to perfection. Vegetarian and protein-rich, this wrap is bound to be a tasty start to any morning.

Dishes.name: Bacon, Gouda & Egg Sandwich
Dishes.description: Sizzling applewood-smoked bacon and a melty aged Gouda and Parmesan frittata layered on an artisan roll for extra-smoky breakfast goodness.

Dishes.name: Double-Smoked Bacon, Cheddar & Egg Sandwich
Dishes.description: Bacon smoked for 6 hours over hickory wood chips, stacked with a fluffy egg patty, topped with a creamy melted slice of sharp cheddar and double-smoked deliciously to fill you up—all on our signature croissant bun.

Dishes.name: Turkey Bacon & Cage-Free Egg White Sandwich
Dishes.description: Sizzling reduced-fat turkey bacon and wholesome cage-free egg whites are paired with the rich creaminess of melted, reduced-fat white cheddar cheese on a wheat English muffin. So good and surprisingly, only 230 calories.

Dishes.name: Sausage, Cheddar & Egg Sandwich
Dishes.description: A savory sausage patty, fluffy eggs and aged cheddar cheese served on a perfectly toasty English muffin. An iconic sandwich that reminds you why you love breakfast.

Dishes.name: Avocado Spread
Dishes.description: Spruce up your sandwich or sous vide egg bites with avocado mixed with a touch of spices and lime. This avocado spread is made using a high-pressure process designed to maintain freshness without the use of heat, additives or preservatives.

Dishes.name: Bacon & Gruyere Sous Vide Egg Bites
Dishes.description: Applewood-smoked bacon and aged Gruyère Monterey Jack cheeses folded into cage-free eggs and cooked using the French "sous vide" technique to create a velvety texture that's full of flavor.

Dishes.name: Egg White and Roasted Pepper Egg Bites
Dishes.description: Cage-free egg whites combined with Monterey Jack cheese, spinach and fire-roasted red peppers and cooked using the French "sous vide" technique to create a velvety texture that's full of flavor.

Dishes.name: Kale & Portabella Mushroom Egg Bites
Dishes.description: Chopped kale and portabella mushrooms delicately folded into cage-free eggs with Monterey Jack cheese and cooked using the French "sous vide" technique to create a velvety texture that's full of flavor.

Dishes.name: Roasted Ham, Swiss & Egg Sandwich
Dishes.description: Take hickory-smoked ham and nutty, melty Swiss cheese layered on a flaky, buttery croissant and you’ve got the perfect wakeup call.

Dishes.name: Berry Trio Parfait
Dishes.description: Nonfat vanilla yogurt combined with sliced strawberries, whole blueberries, raspberries and topped with a crisp honey-oat granola.

Dishes.name: Plain Bagel
Dishes.description: Our classic soft, chewy and thick New York–style bagel: Whether toasted or not, or with a smear of cream cheese or not, each bite tastes of authentic-baked goodness.

Dishes.name: Everything Bagel
Dishes.description: Our signature New York–style bagel topped with onion, garlic, salt, poppy and sesame seeds.

Dishes.name: Avocado Spread
Dishes.description: Spruce up your sandwich or sous vide egg bites with avocado mixed with a touch of spices and lime. This avocado spread is made using a high-pressure process designed to maintain freshness without the use of heat, additives or preservatives.

Dishes.name: Chocolate Cake Pop
Dishes.description: Chocolate cake mixed with chocolate buttercream, dipped in chocolatey coating and topped with sugar sprinkles create this wonderfully reimagined dessert on a stick.

Dishes.name: Cookies & Cream Cake Pop
Dishes.description: Chocolate cake blended with creamy, sandwich-cookie buttercream and cookie bits, dipped in white-chocolaty coating and finished with dark-chocolaty cookie crumb. –Vegetarian.

Dishes.name: Birthday Cake Pop
